Notes:

When second button is selected as jump, up remains active to go up underwater and control
the toy. For simplicity's sake, when the character is touching the water or in the water, both
button AND jump go up (this is for the mixed case when character is knee-deep in the water.
He goes up, then jumps when meets the surface. It would have been unpractical to forbid usage of second button to jump in
that case)

CD남 version never blocked "up" for jump but allowed reverse & forward joypad buttons to
perform the exact same operation. You can choose to leave controls as-is, or use blue button
for jump/swim.


